0.1.3 2015-10-06

 - Add PKCS#12 support
 - Add sign method for CA

0.1.2 2014-10-06

 - Set RSA block cipher to AES256
 - Don't encrypt private key unless a password is defined.
 - Load key if key file already exists when create is called.

